# Dental Prosthetics Lab Management App

## Project Overview
This is a Next.js 14 app for managing dental prosthetics lab orders. It handles order creation, deadline calculation, urgency levels, pickup/delivery logistics, and clinic management.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14 (App Router, TypeScript)
- PostgreSQL via Supabase
- Prisma v5 ORM
- Tailwind CSS
- date-fns for date manipulation

## Business Rules

### Clinic Access Levels
- NEW clinics: can only request REPARACAO, ACRESCIMO_DENTE, ACRESCIMO_GANCHO, REBASE, CONTENCAO
- ACTIVE clinics: have access to all work types

### Urgency Levels
- NORMAL: pickup by 10:00, delivery same day (18:00-19:00 Mon/Wed/Fri, 17:00-17:30 Tue/Thu)
- SUPER_URGENCIA_MANHA: pickup by 10:00, delivery by 13:00 same day
- SUPER_URGENCIA_TARDE: pickup at 13:00, delivery end of day
- Super urgency only available for: REPARACAO, ACRESCIMO_DENTE, ACRESCIMO_GANCHO, REBASE, CONTENCAO
- All urgent orders require manual admin approval
- There is a configurable daily limit for super urgent orders

### Deadline Rules
- All deadlines use working days only (no weekends, no Portuguese public holidays)
- If order placed before or at 10:00 → day 0 is today
- If order placed after 10:00 → day 0 is next working day
- CERA, MOLDEIRA: 3 working days
- PROVA: 3 working days
- TRABALHO_PRONTO, ORTODONTIA: 5 working days
- PROVA_ESQUELETO, ESQUELETO_FLEXIVEL, SOLDADURA, ACRESCIMO_GANCHO_FUNDIDO: no fixed deadline (outsourced)

### Delivery Windows
- Monday, Wednesday, Friday: 18:00 – 19:00
- Tuesday, Thursday: 17:00 – 17:30

### Order Status Flow
PEDIDO_FEITO → RECOLHIDO → EM_PRODUCAO → CONCLUIDO → ENTREGUE
Special states: DEVOLVIDO, EM_ESPERA (for incomplete requirements)

### Work Types
Core (available to all clinics):
- REPARACAO, ACRESCIMO_DENTE, ACRESCIMO_GANCHO, REBASE, CONTENCAO

Extended (active clinics only):
- CERA, MOLDEIRA, PROVA, PROVA_ESQUELETO, ESQUELETO_FLEXIVEL
- TRABALHO_PRONTO, ORTODONTIA, SOLDADURA, ACRESCIMO_GANCHO_FUNDIDO

Outsourced (no fixed deadline):
- PROVA_ESQUELETO, ESQUELETO_FLEXIVEL, SOLDADURA, ACRESCIMO_GANCHO_FUNDIDO

## Database
- Prisma schema is in prisma/schema.prisma
- All models use cuid() for IDs
- Soft deletes are not implemented yet

## File Structure
src/
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/login/
│   ├── (dashboard)/admin/
│   ├── (dashboard)/clinica/
│   └── api/
├── lib/
│   ├── prisma.ts
│   ├── supabase.ts
│   └── dates.ts
├── components/
│   ├── ui/
│   └── orders/
└── types/
    └── index.ts

## Code Conventions
- Always use TypeScript with strict types
- Use Prisma for all database operations, never raw SQL
- Use date-fns for all date manipulation
- All API routes go in src/app/api/
- Use server components by default, client components only when necessary
- Never expose sensitive data to the client
- Always validate inputs on the server side